{"tid":736442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警棍毆途人罪成　朱經緯上訴下月8日審","createTime":"2018-07-10T08:55:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T09:18:16.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1045cf14349fdc5536bfae7591e3f3f853135b23","tid":736442,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180710/s00001/206f72d7ca8f075e73d6679ba10aacae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180710%2Fs00001%2F206f72d7ca8f075e73d6679ba10aacae.jpg&h=7f03ab49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n退休警司朱經緯2014年佔領行動期間，在旺角執勤時以警棍毆打途人頸部，早前被裁定一項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪罪成，被判囚3個月。司法機構網頁顯示，其上訴案已排期下月8日審理，預計需時兩天。<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯今年初被判囚後，隨即就定罪及判刑提出上訴，獲准保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n主任裁判官錢禮於判刑時指出，警務人員有責任維護法紀、預防罪案發生，但朱經緯在執勤時犯案，判刑必須具阻嚇力，防止其他警務人員仿效，以挽回公眾對警隊的信心。即使案發時警隊因處理佔領事件而備受壓力，但壓力並不是犯案的辯解，考慮整體案情後，認為判囚是合適選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180710/s00001/1531210501712\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180710%2Fs00001%2F1531210501712&d=yJ2kETKxjOjjyTvR2w%2FLZI9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=73adc7a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180710%2Fs00001%2F1531210501712&h=3fe93083\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180710/s00001/1531210501712</a>"},{"pid":"e0b9835821ce2283b1065b2c1b38e42c79ce263c","tid":736442,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89f8dd9f3b3ec9a83cb9bce80a6f6152cb57bdbb","tid":736442,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:05:03.000Z","msg":"朱西緯乃柒俠五義，乃真英烈也，唔單止要即時釋放，仲要封佢做護國大將軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8262d56a83595aa37b27fae8be833e09b409b705","tid":736442,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0b9835821ce2283b1065b2c1b38e42c79ce263c","tid":736442,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:01:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:14:18.000Z","msg":"五毛dewi"},{"pid":"0a4d29596be2fe41b74a0cd37266dac47ea5c208","tid":736442,"uid":144843,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a2200d5680fc2383a2da75a452fd90e5ce6f812a","tid":736442,"uid":62837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T09:18:16.000Z","msg":"打柒班仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}